    {
      "id": "963a535a-bc07-42d4-86ef-4f378a2bff1d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use RNNs to predict whether a student will succeed or not. Experiment is performed on all students of a university, regardless of the course. Authors claim to achieve good performance even though performance is unspecified.",
