    {
      "id": "12a4750c-f3ba-8051-bc1c-e6132a44e120",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The reason for a course -agnostic approach comes from the fact that going course-specific would require cutting courses and any new course would not be able to start with a model already available. The paper, thus, proposes a RNN-based course-agnostic model to perform the task.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "12a4750c-f3ba-8051-bc1c-e6132a44e120",
        "parent": {
