    {
      "id": "12a4750c-f3ba-80cd-af98-d6dcfc91965d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors decide to use RNN-based models to make the prediction. They also decide to make a comparison with other models, specifically a regressor that predicts the average grade on exams and a Random Forest. Results show that the LSTM models are the ones who achieve the lowest MSE.",
